MM8D - Growing house and irrigation controlling and remote monitoring system
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. About software
-----------------

  It is a contoller software for MM8D system. MM8D system contents up to
eight MM6D remote controlled switching devices, eight MM7D air quality
measuring device, one MM9A irrigation controller, one MM8D interface
board and a PC or Raspberry Pi.  MM6Ds and MM7Ds connects via wireles
LAN, MM9A and others (auxiliary contact of overcurrent breakers, rain
sensor and LEDs) via MM8D interface board.

 You can view actual status with a browser application and administrate
it with SSH client.

Requirements:

  Hardware: Raspberry Pi 3 Model B.
  Software: Raspbian OS Lite,
            Apache webserver,
            GNUPlot,
            Perl,
            Python3.

  Hardware: PC with a paralel port.
  Software: Debian GNU/Linux operation system,
            Apache webserver,
            GNUPlot,
            Perl,
            Python3.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
------------------------------------------
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  Raspbian OS:      mm8d-sw-0.3-armhf.tar.gz

                    mm8d-eec_0.3-1_armhf.deb
                    mm8d-sw_0.3-1_armhf.deb
                    mm8d-web_0.3-1_all.deb

  Debian GNU/Linux: mm8d-sw-0.3-i386.tar.gz
                    mm8d-sw-0.3-amd64.tar.gz

                    mm8d-eec_0.3-1_i386.deb
                    mm8d-sw_0.3-1_i386.deb
                    mm8d-eec_0.3-1_amd64.deb
                    mm8d-sw_0.3-1_amd64.deb
                    mm8d-web_0.3-1_all.deb

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm8d-sw.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  $ sudo echo "deb http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  $ sudo wget -q -O - http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  $ sudo apt-get update

  install:
  $ sudo apt-get install mm8d-sw mm8d-eec mm8d-web

